name: MY FIRST DIGITAL ART PIECE EVERR - burnedbyairfryer #01 (revisit)
description:
A re-edit of my first digital collage art piece ever created (/burnedbyairfryer)!

May 26th, 2021- “The one that started it all…or didn’t..”


About 6 months ago now, I started learning photoshop..felt impossible & still so much to learn that I kind have been avoiding out of just struggling with the learning curves & staying comfortable..focusing more on just how can I be as creative with what I know now? I told myself after my 30th birthday I will create & post my first digital art piece. Though I wish this was something I pursued in my early 20s..better late than never, right? I still struggle with digital collage & kind of the identity I want to create for this art practice…but looking back at my process & even where I’ve been heading now..I just still feel a little lost with it…BUT searching & learning has been a hell of a fun ride, and even though my life has been in the rut that it’s been in for the last 5 or so years…I’m glad that I started & only hope I will continue to find my new identity, not just in like the artworks, but life. It’s been tough, but these few months have been the most productive & aligned I’ve ever felt in a long time.

@burnedbyairfryer on instagram piece #01 (revisit) (10/10 on tezos chain)
